body:
Add support for UVM's use of #0 delays, e.g.

```
        virtual task wait_on (bit delta = 0);
                if (on) begin
                        if (delta)
                                #0;
                        return;
                end
                num_waiters++;
                @on;
        endtask
```

in about 27 places in UVM.  For now using -Wno-ZERODLY to get around it, but this will block using UVM eventually.

Note @kbieganski et al
